text: Thanatta Chawong, Thai: ธนัสถา ชาวงษ์ , (born on 19 June 1989 in Thailand) is a Thai association football forward who currently plays for the Damallsvenskan club of Östersunds DFF. She also plays for the Thailand women's national football team. == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Female footballers Thanatta Chawong
